- F-21-5 [unnamed/P1] sk-prompt advertises orderedBundle while declaring no bundle rules, leaving the branch's reachability undefined and making a required manual scenario impossible to specify deterministically.
- F-21-6 [sk-doc-templates/P1] The canonical playbook validator does not recurse into per-feature files, so it cannot enforce seven-hub matrix completeness or the compiled-routing evidence fields.
