   222	| A hub edit silently reverts that hub to legacy | High | Medium | P1 drift-CI fails re-mint-required at edit time; P0 readout shows the drifted state | P1 owner |
   223	| The two hardcoded allowlists diverge | Medium | High | P3 single-sources eligibility to "valid fresh manifest exists"; both predicates derive from it | P3 owner |
