   364	## L3: MILESTONES
   365	
   366	| Milestone | Description | Success Criteria | Target |
   367	|-----------|-------------|------------------|--------|
   368	| M0 | Ruling settled | ADR-001 Accepted in `decision-record.md` (adopt the phased path) | Done |
   369	| M1 | Safe to observe | Flag documented; status and drift classification available; resolver coupling remediated or guarded | P0 |
   370	| M2 | Safe to enforce | Re-mint-required CI catches stale manifests | P1 |
   371	| M3 | Safe to canary | One profile runs flag-on with parity and clean fallback evidence | P2 |
   372	| M4 | Safe to scale | Eligibility is derived from manifest freshness and consumers agree | P3 |
   373	| M5 | Effective default | Seven staged gates pass and `=0` restores legacy serving | P4 |
