    10	# Implementation Plan: create-skill Compiled-Routing Alignment
    11	
    12	<!-- SPECKIT_LEVEL: 2 -->
    13	<!-- SPECKIT_TEMPLATE_SOURCE: plan-core + level2-verify | v2.2 -->
    14	<!--
    15	SELF-CHECK:
    16	- Confirm the plan names the simplest viable approach, affected surfaces, and verification path.
    17	- Match phases to the stated scope; remove setup theater that does not change the outcome.
    18	FAILURE MODES:
    19	- Over-planning, missing rollback, and treating assumptions as dependencies.
