   111	|---------|--------------|----------------|--------------|
   112	| `init_skill.py` | Renders parent hub and metadata | Parse state, call minter for ready, report verified outcome | Temp-directory generator tests |
   113	| `hub-skill-scaffold.md` | Active generated hub template | Insert exact directive | Generated `SKILL.md` text assertion |
   114	| `parent-skill-hub-template.md` | Canonical copy-from template | Insert matching directive | Normalized block equality test |
   115	| create-skill `SKILL.md` | Executable authoring workflow | Ask state, order mint after final routing inputs, name failure behavior | Workflow review |
   116	| README and parent reference | Operator guidance | Add examples and dependency boundary | Documentation consistency check |
   117	| Package validator | Completion gate | Validate directive and, when present, shared freshness state | Positive/negative fixture tests |
   118	| Existing contract test suite | Current path/naming regression coverage | Add two-state onboarding matrix | pytest result |
   119	
   120	Inventories before implementation:
   121	
   122	- Confirm every initializer call site and test that relies on the existing function signature.
   123	- Confirm both parent templates and every documentation pointer to them.
   124	- Confirm the P3 minter and predicate API, including error taxonomy and canonical returned path.
   125	<!-- /ANCHOR:affected-surfaces -->
