   141	- [ ] Update `init_skill.py` to render the hub name in both directive positions.
   142	- [ ] Add the ready-mode canonical mint and shared freshness verification after all router inputs are written.
   143	- [ ] Add explicit legacy and compiled-ready output; fail non-zero without a ready claim on mint/freshness errors.
   144	- [ ] Update create-skill workflow, README, parent reference, and package validation.
   145	
   146	### Phase 3: Verification
