.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-claude-code/references/cli-reference.md:27:Claude Code is Anthropic's official CLI for Claude, providing terminal-based AI coding assistance powered by Claude models (Opus, Sonnet, Haiku). It offers deep reasoning via extended thinking, surgical code editing, schema-validated structured output, agent delegation, and persistent memory — all from the command line.
