ll 5 reference filenames are present in the output, pre/post snapshots match, AND `-p context` is in the dispatched command; FAIL if any reference file is missing or any check fails | (1) Define `[profiles.context]` in config.toml if missing per agent-delegation.md §2; (2) re-run with `2>&1 \| tee`; (3) verify the references folder still has all 5 files: `ls .opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-codex/references/` |
