emory/Redis/CDN has count >= 1, AND a RECOMMENDATION section exists; Step 5: pre/post snapshots match | Profile grep, pre/post snapshots, captured stdout, coverage file, dispatched command line, exit code | PASS if exit 0, all 3 strategies named, scores on 3 axes visible, RECOMMENDATION present, pre/post snapshots match, AND `-p ai-council` is in the dispatched command; FAIL if any check misses | (1) Define `[profiles.ai-council]` in config.toml if missing per agent-delegation.md §2; (2) re-run with `2>&1 \| tee`; (3) inspect output for missing strategies and re-prompt explicitly listing the three options |
