.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-codex/references/codex-tools.md:47:**Built-in diff-aware code review.** The `/review` interactive command analyzes staged changes, recent commits, or branch differences using Codex's reasoning, producing structured review output.
.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-codex/references/codex-tools.md:121:**Compared to Claude Code:** Claude Code has a WebSearch tool that provides search results. Codex's `--search` integrates web browsing directly into the reasoning loop, allowing Codex to use retrieved information immediately in code generation or analysis within the same session.
.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-codex/references/codex-tools.md:320:| **Web search** | `WebSearch` | `--search` flag | Codex integrates browsing into reasoning loop |
.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-codex/references/codex-tools.md:329:| **Models** | 3 (Anthropic) | 1 (OpenAI: GPT-5.5) | Codex skill uses GPT-5.5 at configurable reasoning effort |
.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-codex/references/integration-patterns.md:35:- Codex's strengths (sandbox isolation, `xhigh` reasoning, web search via `--search`) complement the calling AI's strengths
.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-codex/references/integration-patterns.md:277:All tasks dispatch `--model gpt-5.5`. Tune reasoning effort per task type:
.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-codex/references/integration-patterns.md:281:| Architecture analysis | `high` / `xhigh` | `-c model_reasoning_effort="high"` | Complex analysis benefits from depth |
.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-codex/references/integration-patterns.md:282:| Security audit | `high` / `xhigh` | `-c model_reasoning_effort="high"` | Catches subtle vulnerability patterns |
.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-codex/references/integration-patterns.md:283:| Complex planning | `high` / `xhigh` | `-c model_reasoning_effort="high"` | Multi-strategy evaluation |
.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-codex/references/integration-patterns.md:284:| Research synthesis | `high` | `-c model_reasoning_effort="high"` | Better synthesis of findings |
.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-codex/references/integration-patterns.md:285:| Code generation | `medium` (default) | `-c model_reasoning_effort="medium"` | Balanced for code output |
.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-codex/references/integration-patterns.md:286:| Standard review | `medium` (default) | `-c model_reasoning_effort="medium"` | Efficient pattern-based review |
.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-codex/references/integration-patterns.md:287:| Implementation | `medium` (default) | `-c model_reasoning_effort="medium"` | Balanced for spec-to-code |
.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-codex/references/integration-patterns.md:288:| Test generation | `medium` (default) | `-c model_reasoning_effort="medium"` | Solid test structure |
.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-codex/references/integration-patterns.md:289:| Documentation | `medium` (default) | `-c model_reasoning_effort="medium"` | Efficient structured generation |
.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-codex/references/integration-patterns.md:290:| Trivial lookups | `low` / `minimal` | `-c model_reasoning_effort="low"` | Minimize latency and cost |
