.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/spec.md:52:`run-skill-benchmark.cjs` resolves a skill root, runs structural gates, loads scenarios, dispatches router-mode cases, calls `scoreScenario()`/`evaluateRouteGold()`, aggregates, and writes the JSON/Markdown reports. In deterministic Mode A, `executor-dispatch.cjs` selects `router-replay.cjs`. Hub route-gold is enforced by default, but the observed route is still the legacy replay only.
